Treasury Cabinet Secretary Ukur Yataani recommended the reintroduction of the tax, which was scrapped by President Uhuru Kenyatta in July 2020Mwendwa said the proposed tax, if adopted by parliament, will cause a biting financial crisis within the local football sceneGor Mahia chairman Ambrose Rachier and his AFC Leopards counterpart Dan Shkanda are some of the local sports stakeholders, who had Thursday weighed in on the proposed reintroduction of the tax